Integrated Generics Inc presidentElliot Friedman told Reuters the company plans to make astatement late Thursday or early Friday.    Trading in the generic drug company's stock was haltedtoday by the American Stock Exchange because of a pendingannouncement, the exchange said.    The announcement will deal with several events that are"favorable," Friedman said but declined to elaborate. Theannouncement will not be ready until late tomorrow or earlyFriday, he said.    Shares of the Bellport, N.Y. maker and distributor ofgeneric drugs closed at 5-3/8 yesterday, unchanged. They weretrading up 3/8 at 5-3/4 before the halt. Reuter&#3;